.container.advertise-page
  .row.header-row
    .col-md-12
      - if params[:text].present?
        h1.text-center = params[:text]
      - else
        h1.text-center THE 8 MOST AWKWARD BRIDESMAID PHOTOS OF ALL TIME
  .row.mobile-change-order
    .col-md-4.hidden-xs.hidden-sm
      .media-wrap
        = image_tag "landingpages/advertising/ad4-pic1.jpg"
    .col-md-8.paragraph
      h2.para-head Seriously, what were they thinking?
      p Awkward conversations with male strippers, carrying around X-rated bachelorette party toys, puffy-sleeved, meringue dresses, bizarre fur trims, bridezillas and totally awkward poses – bridesmaids have a lot to put up with.
      p Click through the worlds most uncomfortable slideshow of bridal party photos. You have been warned.
      p PSA: Be kind to your bridesmaids. They love you. At least get ‘em a nice dress.

  .row
    .col-md-12
      .carousel-wrap
        .ad-carousel
          .media-wrap
